			-- Number of figures to visualize `Current'.
			-- high_quality: (`rectangle', `label_move_handle', `resizer_top_left', `resizer_top_right', `resizer_bottom_right', `resizer_bottom_left').
			-- low_quality: (`rectangle', `name_label')

